dcterms:description: A path loss model specified by the 3rd Generation Partnership Project (3GPP) for urban macro environments, used to model the ground-to-air channel for UAV communications.
dcterms:title: 3rd Generation Partnership Project (3GPP) Urban Macro (UMa) path loss model

dcterms:description: An urban statistical model developed by the ITU-R for predicting radio propagation in urban environments, utilized in the context of UAV communications.
dcterms:title: ITU-R urban statistical model
